## Delete Existing Device

> Example Request

```shell
curl -X DELETE <%=@api_prefix%>/devices?token=Abc123 \
 -H "W-Token: <%=@wiw_token%>"
```
```php
<?php
$wiw = new Wheniwork("<%=@wiw_token%>");
$result = $wiw->delete("devices?token=Abc123");
?>
```

> Example Response

<% json do %>
